---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title='CV | Omar45'>
  <section class='w-full px-2'>
    <section class='flex items-center justify-between md:mb-5'>
      <h2 class='text-3xl font-semibold sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl'>My CV</h2>
      <button
        onclick="
        window.open('/Omar AbdulRahman CV.pdf', '_blank')
        "
        class='rounded bg-brand-accent-purple px-4 py-2 font-bold text-brand-bg hover:bg-brand-accent-purple-hover'
        >Download PDF</button
      >
    </section>

    <hr class='my-3 opacity-30 md:my-5' />

    <h2 class='mb-2 text-3xl font-bold'>Work Experience</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <h3 class='text-xl font-bold'>Frontend Developer</h3>
        <p class='text-lg'>Freelance</p>
        <p class='italic opacity-60 sm:text-lg'>AUG 2021 - Present</p>
        <p class='text-justify text-lg'>
          I've embarked on a dynamic journey, collaborating with a diverse range
          of clients to bring their digital visions to life. Through my
          expertise in cutting-edge web technologies and a creative approach to
          design, I've contributed to the success of several impactful projects.
          From crafting immersive user interfaces to optimizing user
          experiences, my work reflects a commitment to excellence and
          innovation.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3 class='text-xl font-bold'>Frontend Developer</h3>
        <p class='text-lg'>
          <a href='https://github.com/neararabic'>NEAR in Arabic</a>
        </p>
        <p class='italic opacity-60 sm:text-lg'>AUG 2022 - JAN 2023</p>
        <p class='text-justify text-lg'>
          Developed and deployed several projects during a 3-month internship at
          NEAR, resulting in recognition as the best member of a team of 6.
          Continued as a part-time employee for another 3 months, developing 5
          websites related to blockchains, smart contracts, NFTs, and database
          dashboards.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class='mb-2 mt-8 text-3xl font-bold'>Volunteering</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <h3 class='text-xl font-bold'>Organizer / Photographer</h3>
        <p class='text-lg'>
          <a href='https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100093578463906'
            >React Cairo #3</a
          >
        </p>
        <p class='italic opacity-60 sm:text-lg'>AUG 2023</p>
        <p class='text-justify text-lg'>
          I was responsible for media coverage of the event, as well as
          organizing the event itself.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3 class='text-xl font-bold'>Head of Media Committee</h3>
        <p class='text-lg'>
          <a href='https://www.facebook.com/Humans.FCIS'>Humans of FCIS</a>
        </p>
        <p class='italic opacity-60 sm:text-lg'>AUG 2020 - JAN 2023</p>
        <p class='text-justify text-lg'>
          I did a comprehensive rebranding of the entire student activity's
          identity, while also being responsible for the social media presence
          of the association and photography coverage of events.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3 class='text-xl font-bold'>Head of Media Committee</h3>
        <p class='text-lg'>
          <a href='https://www.facebook.com/acmASCIS/'>acmASCIS</a>
        </p>
        <p class='italic opacity-60 sm:text-lg'>AUG 2020 - AUG 2022</p>
        <p class='text-justify text-lg'>
          I took charge of creating social media designs, organizing digital
          campaigns, designing printables, and coordinating photography
          coverage.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3 class='text-xl font-bold'>Head of Media Committee</h3>
        <p class='text-lg'>
          <a href='https://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=a.1726979610860278'
            >Baladna Initiative</a
          >
        </p>
        <p class='italic opacity-60 sm:text-lg'>JAN 2015 - JAN 2018</p>
        <p class='text-justify text-lg'>
          I assumed a leadership role, guiding a team of 20 skilled calligraphy
          artists during the Cairo International Book Fair, where we wrote the
          visitors' names, adding a personalized touch to the event.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class='mb-2 mt-8 text-3xl font-bold'>Education</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <h3 class='text-xl font-bold'>BSc. Computer Science</h3>
        <p class='text-lg'>Ain Shams University</p>
        <p class='text-lg italic opacity-60'>AUG 2019 - JUL 2023</p>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class='mb-2 mt-8 text-3xl font-bold'>Skills</h2>
    <ul class='list-disc columns-2 md:columns-3 md:text-lg'>
      <li>
        <p>HTML, CSS, Sass</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>JS, ES6</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>React JS</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>Astro</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>TailwindCSS</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>Firebase</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>Responsive Design</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>SEO</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>JSON, APIs</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>GitHub</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>Adobe Illustrator</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>UI / UX</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style lang='scss'>
  ul {
    &:where(.columns-2) {
      li {
        margin-left: 1rem;

        &::marker {
          color: #ff79c6;
        }
      }
    }
    &:not(.columns-2) {
      li {
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        margin-left: 0.5rem;
        padding-top: 0.5rem;
        padding-bottom: 1rem;
        &::before {
          content: '';
          position: absolute;
          top: 0.875rem;
          left: -0.5rem;
          width: 1rem;
          height: 1rem;
          background-color: #ff79c6;
          border-radius: 50%;
        }

        &:not(:last-child)::after {
          content: '';
          position: absolute;
          top: 1.25rem;
          left: -1.5px;
          width: 3px;
          height: 100%;
          background-color: #ff79c6;
        }
      }
    }
  }
  a[href^='http'] {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    padding-right: 1.25rem;

    &:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    &::after {
      content: url('/arrow.svg');
      position: absolute;
      top: 0.25rem;
      right: 0;
      width: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
